<p class="text-lg mt-5">{!! translate('Using this stable token also opens up possibilities for programmable payments through smart contracts. For example, you could set up automated payments, subscriptions, or conditional releases of funds based on predefined criteria, all executed transparently and without intermediaries. This level of automation not only enhances convenience but also builds trust between parties by ensuring that contractual obligations are met reliably and on time.') !!}</p>

